---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(r\"$\\left( x + y \\right)$\")"
---
ROOT@0..22
  PARAGRAPH@0..22
    INLINE_MATH@0..22
      DOLLAR@0..1 "$"
      MATH@1..21
        LEFT_RIGHT@1..21
          CONTROL_WORD@1..6 "\\left"
          WORD@6..7 "("
          MATH@7..14
            WHITESPACE@7..8 " "
            WORD@8..9 "x"
            WHITESPACE@9..10 " "
            WORD@10..11 "+"
            WHITESPACE@11..12 " "
            WORD@12..13 "y"
            WHITESPACE@13..14 " "
          CONTROL_WORD@14..20 "\\right"
          WORD@20..21 ")"
      DOLLAR@21..22 "$"
